_sText:
This map was fun to make. ive put many hours into the making of this. hope you enjoy.

ive placed 50 spawns in this map 25 on each team all in random spots on the floor in front of the stage.
theres 10 songs on this map plus one hidden track. lots of secrets to find in this map.
the stage is complete with a drums, speakers and even lighting thats completely controllable via the lighting board in the control room. ive even made instructions on how to run the lights. 
find the secret rampage button (above the maps by striker texture) and spawn mp5's right into the middle of the action.  
ive hidden other weapons as well, awps deagle scout grenade and m4a1 can all be found in this map. (most backstage)
i have a version of this map without the music player in it. if you would like that map you will have to email me at skatersnc@hotmail.com thanks again, hope you enjoy.

also i would like to thank Shiroko for the amazing cannabis model, i did not make it. i wasnt sure who did. robtronic cleared that up for me. so thanks again for the plant. great work.
